NK003(ga)006:2472: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba b+aid+y+aa d+h+aa ra p+au dzi te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2476: sarba bud+d+ha a d+hish+tha na at+ma tsi ba ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2480: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa ni sarba a r+tha s+aa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2483: gzhon nu mas bkal ba'i skud pa gsum bsgril mdud
NK003(ga)006:2484: pa gsum bor ba'i dbus su bo d+hi tsi'i phreng
NK003(ga)006:2485: ba rdog po gcig bcug pa'i gdu bu mkhrig ma
NK003(ga)006:2486: g.yon pa la gdags par gyur /
NK003(ga)006:2487: bla mas rang gi spyi bor gdugs gzung /
NK003(ga)006:2488: thal mo sbyar nas dkyil 'khor la bskor nas nub sgo nas gdugs dang bcas /
NK003(ga)006:2489: spyi bos btud pa'i mos pa dang bcas /
NK003(ga)006:2490: dkyil 'khor la mgo bo 'dud tsam re byas la /
NK003(ga)006:2491: sngags dang rgyud ni 'dzin gyur pa'i //
NK003(ga)006:2492: slob ma 'di ni phul ba lags //
NK003(ga)006:2495: da ni dkyil 'khor slob dpon gyur //
NK003(ga)006:2496: gsang sngags rgyud kyang 'dzin pa dang //
NK003(ga)006:2497: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK003(ga)006:2498: lha rnams kyang ni kun gyi bkur //
NK003(ga)006:2499: sems can rnams la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK003(ga)006:2500: khyod kyis dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin //
NK003(ga)006:2501: nan tan bskyed de bri bar byos //
NK003(ga)006:2502: sgrub pa po yang rgyud la sbyor //
NK003(ga)006:2504: dkyil 'khor lta ba'i ched bsang gtor bya /
NK003(ga)006:2506: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya nas /
NK003(ga)006:2508: sngags gnyis bzla zhing las bum gyi chus spyi bor bsangs gtor bya /
NK003(ga)006:2510: 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med pa rnam par
NK003(ga)006:2511: dag pa'i 'od kyi dkyil 'khor chen po rten dang
NK003(ga)006:2512: brten par bcas pa mngon sum du mthong bar gyur
NK003(ga)006:2514: 'di na bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa 'od zer dri
NK003(ga)006:2515: ma med pa rnam par dag pa'i 'od kyi dkyil
NK003(ga)006:2516: 'khor chen po mngon sum du bzhugs pa yin te
NK003(ga)006:2517: de yang rin po che du ma las byas pa'i
NK003(ga)006:2518: sa gzhi gser gyi bye ma brdal ba de'i steng
NK003(ga)006:2519: du 'o ma'i rgya mtsho chen po nya lcibs la
NK003(ga)006:2520: sogs pa'i skyon dang bral ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2522: ut+pala la sogs pa'i me tog gis brgyan pa /
NK003(ga)006:2523: rin po che'i bya'i tshogs mang po lding ba /
NK003(ga)006:2524: de'i dbus su ri'i rgyal po ri rab gru bzhi
NK003(ga)006:2525: pa ngos bzhi pa nas rin po che sna bzhi
NK003(ga)006:2526: las grub pa'i them skas kyi phreng bas brgyan pa
NK003(ga)006:2527: / mtha' bskor du dpag bsam gyi shing legs par
NK003(ga)006:2528: 'khrungs pas rnam par rgyal ba'i ba dan stong 'phur
NK003(ga)006:2529: ba rang gi khyad par gyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa
NK003(ga)006:2530: / / ri rab de'i steng du pad+ma'i sdong po
NK003(ga)006:2531: rin po che du mas brgyan pa rin po che
NK003(ga)006:2534: ge sar gyis brgyan pa sbur long gi ze'u 'bru can /
NK003(ga)006:2535: snying po'i thog la dngul gyi ri mos bskor ba
NK003(ga)006:2536: dpag tshad du ma'i khyon can ri rab kyi dbus
NK003(ga)006:2538: de las kyang pad+ma'i d+r+wa ba gzhan brgya stong bye
NK003(ga)006:2539: ba snyed byung ba'i steng du gzhal yas khang gru
NK003(ga)006:2541: sgo rin po che'i rtsig pa nang nas rim pa
NK003(ga)006:2542: bzhin dkar dmar ser ljang nag pa'i rim pa lnga
NK003(ga)006:2546: mda' yab la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyogs mdog dbus dkar /
NK003(ga)006:2551: phyi nas 'dod yon gyi snam bu'i kha khyer gyis bskor ba /
NK003(ga)006:2552: rtse mo rdo rje dang nor bu rin po che'i tog gis spras pa /
NK003(ga)006:2553: mtshan nyid thams cad phun sum tshogs pa /
NK003(ga)006:2554: ye shes kyi snang ba las grub pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2555: nang gi dkyil 'khor gyis shar gyi cha'i dbus su
NK003(ga)006:2556: gdan ser po gru bzhi pa'i steng du pad zla
NK003(ga)006:2557: la bcom ldan 'das dpal sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog
NK003(ga)006:2559: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK003(ga)006:2560: dpe byed bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa seng ge'i
NK003(ga)006:2561: khri dang pad zla'i gdan la rdo rje'i skyil krung
NK003(ga)006:2562: gis bzhugs pa / phyag gnyis chos kyi 'khor lo'i phyag rgya mdzad pa zhal nub tu bstan pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2563: de'i g.yon ngos lho phyogs su gdan gyi khri zlum
NK003(ga)006:2564: po la pad zla'i steng du phyag na rdo rje
NK003(ga)006:2565: sku mdog sngon po shin tu mdzes pa rgyan thams
NK003(ga)006:2568: g.yon rdo rje 'dzin pa khro bo'i lus kyi nyams la gnas pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2569: de'i mdun nub kyi phyogs su gdan dkyil 'khor zlum
NK003(ga)006:2570: po'i steng du khyab 'jug nag po lag pa bzhi
NK003(ga)006:2571: pa / g.yas na 'khor lo dang dung /
NK003(ga)006:2572: g.yon na be con dang ral gri thogs pa nam
NK003(ga)006:2573: mkha' lding gi gdan la bzhugs pa rgyan thams cad
NK003(ga)006:2574: kyis brgyan pa'o // de'i g.yon bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK003(ga)006:2575: thad du dkyil 'khor zlum po'i steng du drag po
NK003(ga)006:2576: dmar po mgrin pa sngon po /
NK003(ga)006:2577: lag pa g.yas na mdung rtse gsum pa /
NK003(ga)006:2578: g.yon na ral gri thogs pa /
NK003(ga)006:2579: glang khyu mchog la zhon pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2580: de'i g.yon du tshogs bdag sku mdog sngon po /
NK003(ga)006:2581: g.yas na rdo rje g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
NK003(ga)006:2583: phyir dgye ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2584: lha de gsum zhal shar du gzigs pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2585: shar gyi bcom ldan 'das kyi byang phyogs su gdan
NK003(ga)006:2586: zlum po la pad zla'i steng du 'phags pa spyan
NK003(ga)006:2587: ras gzigs dbang phyug rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa
NK003(ga)006:2588: / ston ka'i 'dam bu'i mdog ltar dkar ba pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK003(ga)006:2591: sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK003(ga)006:2592: phyi'i snam bu'i grwa bzhir pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK003(ga)006:2593: de'i steng du spos chus bkang ba'i bum pa dkar po mgul chings kha rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK003(ga)006:2594: de lta bu'i 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med
NK003(ga)006:2595: par rnam par dag pa'i 'od kyi dkyil 'khor chen
NK003(ga)006:2596: po dang brten par bcas pa mngon sum du mthong
NK003(ga)006:2597: bar gyur / gzungs dang snying po rnams kyang klog dgos pas 'di ltar ro //
NK003(ga)006:2600: pa ri shud+d+he ma na si /
NK003(ga)006:2601: a b+h+y+aa tsi ta pra tish+thi ta nam /
NK003(ga)006:2602: na mo b+ha ga wa te /
NK003(ga)006:2603: a mri ta a yur+sha s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2605: sarba ta th+aa ga ta shud+d+he a yur bi shwa d+ha ni /
NK003(ga)006:2606: sam ha ra sam ha ra /
NK003(ga)006:2607: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+air+ya ba le na pra ti sam ha ra a yu /
NK003(ga)006:2609: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya /
NK003(ga)006:2612: bo d+ha ya bo d+ha ya /
NK003(ga)006:2613: ma ma sarba p+aa pam a wa ra na bi shud+d+he /
NK003(ga)006:2616: hu ru hu ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2617: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma la bi shwa d+ha ni /
NK003(ga)006:2618: ru d+ha ba le pra ti sams+k+aa ra /
NK003(ga)006:2619: ta th+aa ga ta d+h+aa tu d+ha re /
NK003(ga)006:2622: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a d+hish+tha na a d+hish+thi te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2623: a mri tot+b+ha wa ud+b+ha wa h'u phata /
NK003(ga)006:2624: dzi dzi dzi n+aam ga ti ya te de ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2625: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK003(ga)006:2626: na mahtsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK003(ga)006:2627: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK003(ga)006:2630: gri h+na p+aa ya gri h+na p+aa ya h+aum /
NK003(ga)006:2631: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga w+aa na bid+y+aa r+aa dza h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2632: na mo rat+na t+r+aa y+aa ya s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2633: na mahtsan+da badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2634: ma h+aa yak+sha se na ba ti s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2635: na mahtsan+da pra mar+d+ha n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2636: hi ri mi ri ti ri n+ai s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2637: na mo badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2638: lo la tsakra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2639: pa shu pa ti n+ai la kan+tha u ma b+r+ai ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2640: na mo badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2641: b+h+ra ma ra ti ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2642: zhes me tog gi sa snyim pa bkang nas bla ma dang lha la dbul bar mos /
NK003(ga)006:2643: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdo bklag
NK003(ga)006:2644: dgos pas 'di skad bdag gis nas bstod do'i bar
NK003(ga)006:2647: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK003(ga)006:2648: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK003(ga)006:2649: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang ni //
NK003(ga)006:2650: rig sngags gsang sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK003(ga)006:2651: dad pas rab tu brten par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2652: rtag par phyag rgya chen po la //
NK003(ga)006:2653: khyad par du yang mos par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2654: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo dang //
NK003(ga)006:2655: bla ma la yang gus par byos //
NK003(ga)006:2656: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK003(ga)006:2657: dus mtshams rtag tu mchod par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2658: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK003(ga)006:2659: rtag tu glo bur mchod par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2660: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i phyir //
NK003(ga)006:2661: rab tu brtan pa nye bar bzhag /
NK003(ga)006:2662: theg pa la ni dga' rnams kyis //
NK003(ga)006:2663: bsod nams bdag la nan tan bskyed //
NK003(ga)006:2664: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad pa yi //
NK003(ga)006:2665: gsang sngags spyod la brtson par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2666: gsang sngags rgyud las bstan pa yi //
NK003(ga)006:2667: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK003(ga)006:2668: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK003(ga)006:2669: sngags dang phyag rgya mi sbyin no //
NK003(ga)006:2670: gsang sngags rgyud ni legs bsrung zhing //
NK003(ga)006:2671: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bya //
NK003(ga)006:2673: dam tshig de rnams bsrung snyam nas /
NK003(ga)006:2674: gtso bo ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK003(ga)006:2675: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyi //
NK003(ga)006:2677: lha dang bla ma la phyag gsum gsum btsal nas /
NK003(ga)006:2678: ci 'byor ba'i yon phul bsam la /
NK003(ga)006:2679: bdag la rig sngags stsal du gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2681: lha dang bla ma'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK003(ga)006:2682: la sngags kyi phreng ba gnas pa las mar me
NK003(ga)006:2683: gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul du byung nas rang
NK003(ga)006:2684: gi snying ga'i zla ba la gnas par gyur /
NK003(ga)006:2687: pa ri shud+d+he ma na si /
NK003(ga)006:2688: a b+h+ya tsi ta pra tash+thi n+aam /
NK003(ga)006:2689: na mo b+ha ga wa te /
NK003(ga)006:2690: a mri ta a yur+sha s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2692: sarba ta th+aa ga ta shud+d+he a yur bi sho d+ha ni /
NK003(ga)006:2693: sam ha ra sam ha ra /
NK003(ga)006:2694: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+air+ya ba le na pra ti sam ha r+aa yuh s+aa ra s+aa ra /
NK003(ga)006:2695: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya /
NK003(ga)006:2698: bo d+ha ya bo d+ha ya /
NK003(ga)006:2699: ma ma sarba p+aa pam +aa wa ra na bi shud+d+he /
NK003(ga)006:2702: hu ru hu ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2704: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma la bi shwa d+ha ni /
NK003(ga)006:2705: ru d+ha ba le pra ti sams+k+aa ra /
NK003(ga)006:2706: ta th+aa ga ta d+h+aa tu d+ha re /
NK003(ga)006:2709: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a d+hish+tha na a d+hish+thi te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2710: dzi dzi dzi nam ga ti ya ti da ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2711: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2712: na mo tsan+da badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2713: ma h+aa yak+sha se n+aa pa te s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2714: na mash+tsan+da pra mar+d+ha na ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2715: hi ri mi ri ti ri n+ai s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2716: na mo badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2717: lo la tsakra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2718: pa shu pa ti ni la kan+tha u ma b+r+ai ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2719: na mo badz+ra p+aa ni s+ya /
NK003(ga)006:2720: b+ha ma ra ti ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2724: bcom ldan 'di la bsnyen pa dang //
NK003(ga)006:2726: bcom ldan bdag gis bzung lags kyis //
NK003(ga)006:2727: bdag la 'go bar mdzad du gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2729: spyi bor bzung ste lha rnams kyi snying po bdun la sogs pa bazla'o //
NK003(ga)006:2731: deng nas brtsams te sogs bya'o //
NK003(ga)006:2733: mtha' rten rgyas par byed na /
NK003(ga)006:2734: gong gi bzlas lung gi mthar bkru byab srung gsum bya ste /
NK003(ga)006:2736: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma la nas /
NK003(ga)006:2738: rdo rje slob ma rnams kyi sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2740: nad thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2741: rims thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2742: gdon thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2743: nye bar 'tshe ba thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2744: dus ma yin pa'i 'chi ba thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2745: 'khon thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2746: grib thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2747: byad thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2748: byur thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2749: skal pa ngan pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2750: ltas ngan pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2751: mtshan ma ngan pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2752: rmi lam ngan pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2753: bkra mi shis pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2754: mtshan mo nag mo'i gdon thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2755: bdud kyi zhags pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2756: gshin rje'i pho nya thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2757: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2759: yang ku sha dang rma bya'i sgros byabs te /
NK003(ga)006:2760: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma la nas /
NK003(ga)006:2762: rdo rje slob ma rnams kyi sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad a pa n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2764: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa thams cad a pa n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2765: zhes pa'i bar brjod la bya ba tshul bya /
NK003(ga)006:2766: na mo rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas
NK003(ga)006:2767: pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka'
NK003(ga)006:2768: bden pa dang / sangs rgyas kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2769: chos kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2770: dge 'dun gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2771: yi dam rgyud sde chen po bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2772: khyad par bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa 'od zer dri
NK003(ga)006:2773: ma med pa'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK003(ga)006:2774: dang / dpal mgon dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2775: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis rdo rje
NK003(ga)006:2776: slob ma 'di rnams kyi nad gdon mi mthun pa'i
NK003(ga)006:2777: phyogs thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du dengs
NK003(ga)006:2779: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya nas /
NK003(ga)006:2781: ces brjod yungs dkar gyis brab /
NK003(ga)006:2784: sangs rgyas rnams ni bdud las rgyal //
NK003(ga)006:2785: chos ni chos ma yin las so //
NK003(ga)006:2786: dge 'dun mu stegs rnams las rgyal //
NK003(ga)006:2787: dbang po lha min rnams las rgyal //
NK003(ga)006:2788: nam mkha' lding ni rgya mtsho las //
NK003(ga)006:2789: me ni shing rnams kun las rgyal //
NK003(ga)006:2790: chu ni me las rgyal bar 'gyur //
NK003(ga)006:2791: rlung ni sprin las rgyal bar 'gyur //
NK003(ga)006:2792: rdo rje yis ni rin chen phug /
NK003(ga)006:2793: lha rnams bden par rab tu gnas //
NK003(ga)006:2794: sa yang bden par gnas pa lags //
NK003(ga)006:2795: sangs rgyas dang ni chos kyang bden //
NK003(ga)006:2796: bden par rgyal gyur rdzun ma lags //
NK003(ga)006:2797: bden pa dang bden pa'i tshigs 'di dag gis bdag
NK003(ga)006:2798: cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa thams
NK003(ga)006:2799: cad bdud dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad las
NK003(ga)006:2801: dza ya dza ya su dza ya /
NK003(ga)006:2803: sarba ta th+aa ga ta nas /
NK003(ga)006:2805: spyi bo sogs gnas lngar rdo rje rgya gram du 'jog cing /
NK003(ga)006:2806: rdo rje slob ma rnams kyi sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad rak+sha rak+sha /
NK003(ga)006:2808: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa thams cad rak+sha rak+sha /
NK003(ga)006:2810: rgyal ba sras bcas bden pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK003(ga)006:2811: bdag gis tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab kyis //
NK003(ga)006:2812: 'gro ba 'di la legs par bsrungs zin gyis //
NK003(ga)006:2813: 'di la sus kyang gnod par ma byed cig /
NK003(ga)006:2814: de nas rgyal srid sna bdun /
NK003(ga)006:2815: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi tshigs rnams brjod cing len tshul /
NK003(ga)006:2817: bkra shis gang zhig mchod pa'i lha mo ni //
NK003(ga)006:2818: phyag na gdugs bzang gser gyi yu ba can //
NK003(ga)006:2819: thogs nas rgyal ba'i dbu la mchod pa ltar //
NK003(ga)006:2820: dbu la gdugs kyi bkra shis thob par shog /
NK003(ga)006:2821: mang+ga la tsha tram a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK003(ga)006:2822: bkra shis gang zhig mchod pa'i lha mo ni //
NK003(ga)006:2823: phyag na gser gyi nya mo 'od 'bar ma //
NK003(ga)006:2824: thogs nas rgyal ba'i spyan la mchod pa ltar //
NK003(ga)006:2825: spyan la gser nya'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK003(ga)006:2826: mats+tsha bkra shis gang zhig mchod pa'i lha mo ni //
NK003(ga)006:2827: phyag na pad+ma dmar po 'dab brgyad pa //
NK003(ga)006:2828: thogs nas rgyal ba'i ljags la ljags la pad+ma'i pad+ma bkra shis gang zhig mchod pa'i lha mo ni //
NK003(ga)006:2829: phyag na rin chen bum pa yongs gang ba //
NK003(ga)006:2830: thogs nas rgyal ba'i mgul la mgul la bum pa'i
NK003(ga)006:2831: bkra shis ku m+b+ha bkra shis gang zhig phyag na
NK003(ga)006:2833: thogs nas rgyal ba'i thugs la thugs la dpal be'u'i
NK003(ga)006:2834: bkra shis sh+r+ai pany+tsa bkra shis gang zhig phyag na
NK003(ga)006:2835: rin chen rgyal mtshan yid 'ong ba //
NK003(ga)006:2836: thogs nas rgyal ba'i sku la sku la rgyal mtshan
NK003(ga)006:2837: d+h+wa dza bkra shis gang zhig phyag na chos dung
NK003(ga)006:2839: thogs nas rgyal ba'i gsung la gsung la dung gi
NK003(ga)006:2840: shang+kha bkra shis gang zhig phyag na gser gyi 'khor
NK003(ga)006:2842: thogs nas rgyal ba'i zhabs la zhabs la 'khor lo'i bkra shis mang+ga lam tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK003(ga)006:2843: zhes brjod cing len tshul byas la /
NK003(ga)006:2844: me tog gi char dbab cing bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rgya cher 'don no //
NK003(ga)006:2847: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK003(ga)006:2848: de nas mchod pa sogs bsham /
NK003(ga)006:2851: byin gyis rlob pa sogs sngar bzhin /
NK003(ga)006:2853: khrus nas mar me'i bar gtso bor sum gyur sogs rgyas pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2855: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK003(ga)006:2857: skye ba dran zhing brtse ldan shog /
NK003(ga)006:2858: ces pa'i bar mdun bskyed kyi mchod bstod rgyas pa bzhin /
NK003(ga)006:2860: sgrub khang sgor bsang ba sogs sngar bzhin byas nas stan la 'khod de /
NK003(ga)006:2861: bla ma dang 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med
NK003(ga)006:2862: pa rnam par dag pa'i 'od kyi dkyil 'khor chen
NK003(ga)006:2863: po'i lha tshogs sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i
NK003(ga)006:2864: tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad bdag cag la dgongs
NK003(ga)006:2865: su gsol // khyed rnams la mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK003(ga)006:2866: brtse ba'i thugs rje mdzad pa'i phrin las bsam gyis
NK003(ga)006:2867: mi khyab pa mnga' ba lags pas /
NK003(ga)006:2868: spyir gyi phan bde'i 'byung gnas sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK003(ga)006:2869: pa rin po che phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad
NK003(ga)006:2870: du dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par
NK003(ga)006:2872: bstan pa'i rtsa lag dpal ldan bla ma dam pa gong ma zhi bar gshegs pa rnams dang /
NK003(ga)006:2873: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi thugs
NK003(ga)006:2874: zag med kyi dgongs pa khyad par can gong nas
NK003(ga)006:2875: gong du yongs su rdzogs pa'i phrin las mdzad du
NK003(ga)006:2876: gsol // da lta zhal bzhugs pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi gtsor mdzad /
NK003(ga)006:2877: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'dzin pa'i dge ba'i bshes
NK003(ga)006:2878: gnyen thams cad sku khams bzang zhing sku tshe brtan
NK003(ga)006:2879: par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2880: bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi sdig pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2882: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK003(ga)006:2883: mtho ris dang thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i lam gyi bar du gcod pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2886: shes bya'i sgrib pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2887: gnas skabs su yang las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis 'byung ba'i gnod pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2888: sdug bsngal gyi bye brag gdon chen po bco brgyad dang /
NK003(ga)006:2889: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu dang /
NK003(ga)006:2894: pha rol gyi rigs sngags las gyur pa'i gnod pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK003(ga)006:2897: sa g.yo ba la sogs pa 'byung ba las gyur pa'i gnod pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2899: dgra'i gnod pa la sogs pa 'jigs pa chen po bcu drug dang /
NK003(ga)006:2903: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang /
NK003(ga)006:2905: dus ma yin pa'i 'chi ba'i duhkha dang /
NK003(ga)006:2906: de dag gi rgyu bsam sbyor ngan pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK003(ga)006:2907: khyad par du yang bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod
NK003(ga)006:2908: 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad kyi sngon gyi las
NK003(ga)006:2909: las gyur kyang 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung
NK003(ga)006:2910: ste phyi nang gi nye bar 'tshe ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2911: lus sems la gnod par byed pa'i gdon bgegs dang /
NK003(ga)006:2912: nad la sogs pa lus kyi du khahdang /
NK003(ga)006:2913: sems kyi yid mi bde ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2921: dge ba sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2922: mdor na bdag gzhan sems can thams cad kyi gnas
NK003(ga)006:2923: skabs su mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad nye bar
NK003(ga)006:2924: zhi nas 'og min gyi srid pa'i mthar thug pa'i
NK003(ga)006:2925: 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub mtha' dag 'grub pa dang
NK003(ga)006:2926: / mthar thug sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa
NK003(ga)006:2927: ma lus pa zhi ba'i phyag rgya chen po mchog
NK003(ga)006:2928: gi dngos grub tshe 'di la thob par byin gyis
NK003(ga)006:2929: / brlab tu gsol / bla ma dang bcom ldan
NK003(ga)006:2930: 'das 'phags pa 'od zer dri ma med pa rnam
NK003(ga)006:2931: par dag pa'i 'od kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i lha
NK003(ga)006:2932: tshogs sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang
NK003(ga)006:2933: bcas pa thams cad bdag cag rnams la dgongs su
NK003(ga)006:2934: / brlab tu gsol / gsol // bdag cag rnams
NK003(ga)006:2935: so so skye bor gyur pas nyon mongs pa can
NK003(ga)006:2936: du gyur nas lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa
NK003(ga)006:2937: nyon mongs pa dang 'dres shing bdag med par gyur
NK003(ga)006:2938: pas rnal 'byor la dbang ma thob pas sems bying
NK003(ga)006:2939: / brlab tu gsol / gsol // ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2940: rgod pa'i dbang du gyur te ting nge 'dzin mi
NK003(ga)006:2941: / brlab tu gsol / gsol // ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2942: gsal ba dang / snyigs ma lnga'i dus kyi dbang
NK003(ga)006:2943: gis nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad ma 'byor ba
NK003(ga)006:2944: / brlab tu gsol / gsol // ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2945: gsal ba dang / dang / mchod rdzas med cing
NK003(ga)006:2946: / brlab tu gsol / gsol // ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2947: gsal ba dang / dang / ngan pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2949: shes bzhin ma yin pa'i dbang du gyur nas cho ga lhag pa dang /
NK003(ga)006:2951: ser sna'i dbang gis mchod pa ngan zhing chung ba dang /
NK003(ga)006:2952: gti mug gi dbang gis rgyud sde nas 'byung ba'i
NK003(ga)006:2953: cho ga bzhin du ma lcogs pa la sogs pa
NK003(ga)006:2954: 'khrul zhing nongs pa thams cad bzod par bzhes nas
NK003(ga)006:2955: / bdag cag gi lam dang dngos grub kyi bar
NK003(ga)006:2956: chad du mi 'gyur bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol
NK003(ga)006:2957: / // rdo rje'i sems dpa'i yig brgya lan bdun /
NK003(ga)006:2958: ma 'byor ba dang nyams pa dang //
NK003(ga)006:2959: gang yang bdag rmongs blo yis ni //
NK003(ga)006:2960: bgyis pa dang ni bgyid stsal ba //
NK003(ga)006:2961: de kun mgon pos bzod par gsol //
NK003(ga)006:2962: dge ba'i rtsa ba de yang sems can thams cad thun mong du byas te /
NK003(ga)006:2963: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di dag gis bdag dang sems
NK003(ga)006:2964: can thams cad 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK003(ga)006:2965: pa'i rgud pa thams cad bral bar gyur cig /
NK003(ga)006:2966: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phun sum
NK003(ga)006:2967: tshogs pa thams cad dang yang dag par bden pa'i
NK003(ga)006:2968: bde ba dang / mi bde ba nyid kyi mi'i
NK003(ga)006:2969: mchog sangs rgyas su tshe 'di nyid la gyur cig
NK003(ga)006:2970: bde ba dang / / bdag gi dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag gis //
NK003(ga)006:2971: 'jig rten 'dir ni myur du sangs rgyas shog /
NK003(ga)006:2972: 'gro la phan phyir chos rnams ston bgyid cing //
NK003(ga)006:2973: sems can sdug bsngal mang pos gzir las sgrol //
NK003(ga)006:2975: bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK003(ga)006:2976: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK003(ga)006:2977: ji srid mchod pa bdag 'bul na //
NK003(ga)006:2978: de srid bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang bcas pas rdul
NK003(ga)006:2979: tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK003(ga)006:2980: // su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2981: g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pas me tog 'thor zhing brtan bzhugs bya /
NK003(ga)006:2982: bdag gi lha'i sku gzugs zla ba'i steng gi yi ge la thim /
NK003(ga)006:2983: yi ge zla ba la thim /
NK003(ga)006:2984: zla ba rnam smin gyi lus la thim par gyur /
NK003(ga)006:2985: badz+ra ag+ne pra ti pa ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK003(ga)006:2986: rdo rje'i go cha bskon par gyur /
NK003(ga)006:2987: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK003(ga)006:2988: h+aum wa k+ai li h+aum phata /
NK003(ga)006:2992: mgrin pa rnams su go cha byas par gyur //
NK003(ga)006:2993: che ba'i che mchog ston mchog bla na med //
NK003(ga)006:2994: chos rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK003(ga)006:2995: bgegs dang bdud rigs gnod pa'i dgra zhi ste //
NK003(ga)006:2996: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK003(ga)006:2998: thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston chos rje yi //
NK003(ga)006:2999: dkyil chog 'chi med 'byung ba gtsor bton zhing //
NK003(ga)006:3000: lhan thabs mun sel nyin snang zur sdebs pa'i //
NK003(ga)006:3001: rin chen blo gsal bstan skyong chog bsgrigs bzhin //
NK003(ga)006:3002: bklag chog dri med rab gsal bris pa'i dge //
NK003(ga)006:3003: 'gro kun ye shes snang ba rtogs phyir bsngo //
NK003(ga)006:3004: zhes pa 'adi'ang chog bsgrigs 'od zer phreng ba ltar
NK003(ga)006:3005: 'don bder bklag chog mar bkod pa rdo rje 'chang
NK003(ga)006:3006: ba 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po'i bka' drin gyis
NK003(ga)006:3007: tshul 'di la cung zad blo kha phyogs pa mdo
NK003(ga)006:3008: sngags bstan 'dzin bzang pos spel ba sarba d+aa mang+ga
